%sh
URL=`echo aHR0cHM6Ly9zMy1ldS13ZXN0LTEuYW1hem9uYXdzLmNvbS9pb3QtZGVtby10ZWxlbWV0cnktMS9jYXJfdGVsZW1ldHJ5Lmpzb24udGFyLmd6Cg== | base64 --decode`
#use https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sapdemo/dh_telemetry_demo/master/data/car_telemetry.json.tar.gz

echo $URL
curl -o /root/car_telemetry.json.tar.gz $URL

tar -xvzf /root/car_telemetry.json.tar.gz 

hadoop fs -mkdir /car_telemetrydata
hadoop fs -put /car_telemetry.json /car_telemetrydata

paragraphs.text:
%sh
rm /tmp/s4mat*
URL=`echo aHR0cHM6Ly9yYXcuZ2l0aHVidXNlcmNvbnRlbnQuY29tL3NhcGRlbW8vZGhfdGVsZW1ldHJ5X2RlbW8vbWFzdGVyL2RhdGEvczRtYXRlcmlhbGRhdGEuemlwCg== | base64 --decode`
echo $URL
curl -o /tmp/s4materialdata.zip $URL

rm -R /s4materialdata
mkdir /s4materialdata
unzip -P sap123 /tmp/s4materialdata.zip -d /s4materialdata 

cp -p /s4materialdata/fordatahub/index/SAPHE4/MA/MARA/data.csv /s4materialdata/MARA.csv
cp -p /s4materialdata/fordatahubmbwe/index/SAPHE4/MB/MBEW/data.csv /s4materialdata/MBEW.csv
cp -p /s4materialdata/fordatahubmakt/index/SAPHE4/MA/MAKT/data.csv /s4materialdata/MAKT.csv
cp -p /s4materialdata/fordatahubmarc/index/SAPHE4/MA/MARC/data.csv /s4materialdata/MARC.csv

rm -R /s4materialdata/fordatahub*
hdfs dfs -mkdir /s4data

hdfs dfs -put /s4materialdata/M* /s4data
#remember 777
hdfs dfs -chmod 777 /car_telemetry_solution

hdfs dfs -put /s4materialdata/M* /car_telemetry_solution
hdfs dfs -ls /s4data

URL2=`echo aHR0cHM6Ly9yYXcuZ2l0aHVidXNlcmNvbnRlbnQuY29tL3NhcGRlbW8vZGhfdGVsZW1ldHJ5X2RlbW8vbWFzdGVyL2RhdGEvTU1fTUFDLmNzdgo= | base64 --decode`
echo $URL2
curl -o /tmp/MM_MAC.csv $URL2
hdfs dfs -rm /car_telemetry_solution/MM_MAC.csv
hdfs dfs -put /tmp/MM_MAC.csv /car_telemetry_solution
